# Planning and Task Management

This project uses markdown files for planning and task management. The following conventions should be followed:

## File Structure

- `plan.md` - Main planning document
- `TODO.md` - Current tasks and todos
- `CHANGELOG.md` - Version history and changes

## Task Format

Tasks should be formatted as follows:

```markdown
## [Task Name]

### Description
Brief description of the task

### Requirements
- Requirement 1
- Requirement 2

### Implementation Notes
- Note 1
- Note 2

### Status
- [ ] Not Started
- [ ] In Progress
- [ ] Completed
```